JDY8XkebaeA.title: Join Us Today
JDY8XkebaeA.description: Free Fire - Battlegrounds is a survival, third-person shooter game in the form of battle royale. 50 players parachute onto a remote island, where there is only one winner - the last man standing. Players freely choose starting position, grab weapons and supplies to bolster your chances of survival in the battlegrounds. The battleground shrinks as time goes on, forcing players to engage each other in a tactical and diverse environment.

5n8NDyjLc24.title: Elite Pass Season 7 - Steampunk Revolution
5n8NDyjLc24.description:
Orphaned at the hands of terrible witches, Maxim and Misha grew up together and learned the ways of witch-hunting.

On their mission to investigate the alleged abduction of lost children by the wicked witches, the leads took them to the top of the Notre Dame Cathredal - where they found the witches in the midst of extracting the soul of Kelly. 

How will their mission end? 😲 Find out more about the Steampunk Revolution soon... 

In the meantime, you can pre-order the new Elite Pass and earn yourselves an exclusive Steampunk Backpack (only available when you pre-order)!
